      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 125,
      "message": "I checked with a boxed boolean method. In Eclipse anyway, the convention is that boxed boolean values get gettters generated using the \"get\" prefix:\n\nprivate Boolean myBoolean;\n\nresults in a generated getter as follows:\n\npublic Boolean getMyBoolean() {\n    return myBoolean;\n}",
